#  Rock Paper Scissors

A simple and interactive Rock Paper Scissors game built with JavaScript.

##  Features

* Play using buttons or keyboard (R / P / S)
* Score tracking with localStorage
* Reset confirmation system

##  Tech

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript

##  Note

This project was originally built following a tutorial, then redesigned and improved.

